---
---
<section class="page-container section-spacer">
  <div class="glow-line-magenta"></div>
  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr; gap: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow fade-in" style="color: var(--color-magenta);">safety</p>
      <h2 class="fade-in-up delay-1">The no-list.</h2>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0;">
        <div class="fade-in-up delay-2" style="padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.875rem;">No ads</div>
        <div class="fade-in-up delay-3" style="padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.875rem;">No tracking</div>
        <div class="fade-in-up delay-4" style="padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.875rem;">No analytics</div>
        <div class="fade-in-up delay-5" style="padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.875rem;">No cloud sync</div>
        <div class="fade-in-up delay-6" style="padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.875rem;">No accounts</div>
        <div class="fade-in-up delay-7" style="padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.875rem;">No social features</div>
        <div class="fade-in-up delay-8" style="padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.875rem;">No camera access</div>
        <div class="fade-in-up delay-8" style="padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.875rem;">No microphone access</div>
        <div class="fade-in-up delay-8" style="padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.875rem;">No location data</div>
        <div class="fade-in-up delay-8" style="padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.875rem;">No data selling</div>
        <div class="fade-in-up delay-8" style="padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.875rem;">No browser dependency</div>
        <div class="fade-in-up delay-8" style="padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-ink-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.875rem;">No app store gatekeepers</div>
      </div>
      <div class="fade-in-up delay-8" style="margin-top: 3rem;">
        <p class="body-small" style="font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 0.9375rem;">elly is designed for care, with care. Encrypted at rest. Local token auth via OS keyring. Loopback-only network binding. Full threat model in SECURITY.md.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
